data.description: Experience modern elegance in this 4-bedroom, 2-bath one-story home with an office off the entryway, nestled in charming Justin, Texas. The open concept design, fireplace, and kitchen island create a cozy ambiance, while stainless steel appliances and a mix of wood, tile, and carpet flooring add style. Enjoy the convenience of nearby shopping and dining and relax on the back patio. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort, sophistication, and practicality for your lifestyle. Located on a corner lot, right across from the community pool. Other community amenities offered are walking trails, playground, and a catch-and-release fishing pond.  Recently updated flooring, solar panels, and windows. Solar panels are owned with payment terms.
